Passenger verification procedures require shuttle companies to confirm passenger identity, destination details, and payment status before departure. This process takes 5-10 minutes per passenger under normal circumstances, but complications with reservations, payment methods, or destination changes can extend verification time significantly. With 8-12 passengers per shuttle, total verification time alone can consume 45-60 minutes.

